{"tid":1876931,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"鍊成咗腎者之石 點算","createTime":"2020-02-12T17:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T15:14:03.000Z","uid":30831,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb88ec1caf920d13375e54795e3e33c227f2d54","tid":1876931,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"最近去照到有幾粒細細地嘅腎石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又驗到尿有血<br />\n點解廿歲人就鍊成咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇腎之鍊金術師前輩教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪好難斷 會唔會真係腎者之石咁痛不欲生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有乜做到<br />\n<br />\n前排都打算做多啲運動 肺炎出黎日日都留係屋企做廢人<br />\n已經係咁飲水 啲尿味好重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae15bd5ce6e74f2bb9d7f3aa1dc9b826a6aec76","tid":1876931,"uid":317305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:21:22.000Z","msg":"平時唔撚飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />把口肯定好撚臭"},{"pid":"23920227dde45584ceef0c9aa579fc7b98d9f615","tid":1876931,"uid":199902,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"食嘢清淡啲、少鹽(唔係零鹽份)呢啲應該啊媽係女人<br />\n另外得閒就做多啲帶氧運動啦<br />\n亡羊補牢始終唔係萬能"},{"pid":"420d567415ee36aee1b57bb0e454193e085aab99","tid":1876931,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:32:28.000Z","msg":"btw呢段時間被迫喺屋企嘅話，跳繩係唔錯嘅選擇，強度高、佔用空間細，小心保持正確姿勢保護膝頭就ok"},{"pid":"49606af9ced20751541ea815c545c590ea5373d9","tid